{"article_id":"RrH92mWY7XpQcKkO","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Beto O ' Rourke may have inadvertently got the ball rolling this week on an emerging litmus test for Democrats","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"eyeing the White House in 2020","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"when he said","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"he \" absolutely \" supports tearing down the existing barriers along the southern border with Mexico .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Since then , the other Democrats","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"eyeing the 2020 Democratic nomination","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"are facing calls","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"to say","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"whether they agree .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"And some are now expressing an openness to it ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"as they work to appeal to a liberal base","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"that argues","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"the wall is immoral .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"\" Curious to know","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"if @ KamalaHarris , @ CoryBooker , @ ewarren , @ JulianCastro , @ gillibrandny and @ amyklobuchar agree with @ BetoORourke","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"that we should tear down the wall","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"that already exists at the border ? \"","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"tweeted Brad Parscale , Trump ' s re-election campaign manager .","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"O ' Rourke , the former Texas Democratic congressman and potential presidential candidate , called for the destruction of the El Paso wall","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"after the White House said","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"President Trump would declare a national state of emergency","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"to fund the remainder of his border wall project .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"During an interview in his hometown on Thursday , MSNBC host Chris Hayes asked O'Rourke :","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"`` If you could ,","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"would you take the wall down here","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"-- knock it down ? ''","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"BETO SAYS","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"HE 'ABSOLUTELY ' SUPPORTS DESTROYING EXISTING WALLS ON SOUTHERN BORDER `","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"` Yes , absolutely , ''","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"answered O'Rourke ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"who is widely thought to be a potential candidate in 2020","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"but has not formally announced his intention","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"to run .","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"`` I 'd take the wall down . ''","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"And on Friday , at least one Democrat in the 2020 field signaled","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"they are open to it .","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"GILLIBRAND ON CALL TO TEAR DOWN BORDER WALL :","depth":4},{"id":37,"text":"'IF IT MAKES SENSE ,","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"I COULD SUPPORT IT ' `","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"` I could look at it","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"and see which part he means and why","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"and","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"if it makes sense","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"I could support it , \"","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"New York Sen. Kirsten Gillibrand told Fox News in New Hampshire on Friday .","depth":4},{"id":45,"text":"Meanwhile , Republicans expressed disbelief over O ' Rourke ' s comments ,","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"while signaling","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"they believe","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"they could use the issue","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"to paint Democrats as extreme and pro-open borders .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"\" Correct me","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"if I am wrong ,","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"but did Beto say","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"he would tear down existing border fencing and walls ? \"","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"tweeted Texas Sen. John Cornyn ,","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"who is up for re-election in 2020 .","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"Some Democrats have encouraged O ' Rourke to challenge Cornyn","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"if he doesn ' t run for president .","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"\" Give Beto O ' Rourke points for honesty :","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"he admits","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"that he wants to tear down existing border walls","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"& have totally open borders , \"","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"said Arkansas Republican Sen. Tom Cotton .","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"\" At least he ' ll say","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"what most Democrat politicians believe . \"","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"RNC chairwoman Ronna McDaniel used O ' Rourke ' s comments","depth":5},{"id":66,"text":"to say","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"it ' s proof","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"Democrats are \" the party of open borders . \"","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"While O ' Rourke was the first likely 2020 presidential candidate","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"to call for tearing down walls ,","depth":5},{"id":71,"text":"other lesser-known Democrats in recent weeks have suggested","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"they support the idea .","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"In an interview in January for example , Democratic Texas Rep. Veronica Escobar told CNN","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"that `` we know walls do n't work ,","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"that they do n't stop drugs ,","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"that they do n't stop migration . ''","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"Escobar also suggested","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"she was open to destroying existing walls ,","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"remarking","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"that they are `` really ugly '' and `` monuments to division . ''","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"HOYER SAYS","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"BORDER WALLS 'OBVIOUSLY ' WORK ,","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"REJECTS PELOSI 'S SUGGESTION","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"THAT BARRIER IS 'IMMORALITY '","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"But not all Democrats have embraced the idea :","depth":5},{"id":86,"text":"House Majority Leader Steny Hoyer , D-Md. , said during an interview on Fox News ' `` Special Report with Bret Baier '' last month","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"that border walls `` obviously '' work in some areas ,","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"and he rejected suggestions","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"that barriers should be removed","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"where they already exist .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":181,"left":135,"right":180,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":135,"left":126,"right":134,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":126,"left":108,"right":125,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":103,"right":107,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":94,"right":102,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":92,"right":93,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":92,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":102,"left":98,"right":101,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":98,"left":96,"right":97,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":95,"right":6,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":95,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":101,"left":9,"right":100,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":10,"right":99,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":107,"left":106,"right":17,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":13,"right":105,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":105,"left":14,"right":104,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":104,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":123,"right":124,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":123,"left":111,"right":122,"relation":"context","nuclearity":